League Center is a Chrome Extension that provides updates and information on soccer standings from various leagues and tournaments around the world. With this extension, soccer fans can stay on top of the latest standings. 

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install the League Center extension and set the new tab search to that provided by the service. The search will be powered by Microsoft Bing.

With a user-friendly interface and fast performance, League Center is the perfect companion for soccer fans who want to stay up-to-date on all the action. Other features also include checking the weather and seeing the date.
